Scope of this license
---------------------

This license applies to the Big Ambitions Mod Template source code and
assets in this repository, including:

  - Editor tooling under `Assets/Editor/` (Mod Builder,
    Welcome window, and related scripts)
  - The sample mod under `Assets/Mods/FalconToy/`
  - Project settings, documentation, and build scripts

This license does NOT grant any rights to Big Ambitions, Big Ambitions' own
DLLs, or any third-party Unity Asset Store plugins that Big Ambitions ships
with. Those DLLs are not distributed with this template. Instead, the
Welcome window imports them from your own local Steam install of Big
Ambitions into `Assets/_BaDependencies/GameDlls/` on first setup. Your
right to use those DLLs is governed by the respective licenses of Big
Ambitions (Hovgaard Games), the original Asset Store authors, and Valve's
Steam Subscriber Agreement — not by this MIT license.
